08.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一些<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/old-school-runescape"><em>Old School RuneScape</em></a>帐户已被不良行为者劫持，使他们能够将受害者的帐户附加到黑客的<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/steam">Steam</a>帐户。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/how-farming-in-old-school-runescape-fixed-my-morning-misery-3380318">“Old School RuneScape”中的农业如何解决我早上的痛苦</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/jagex">Jagex</a>在<em>Old School RuneScape</em>网站上的一篇<a href="https://secure.runescape.com/m=news/regarding-character-linking-concerns?oldschool=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">新闻文章</a>中宣布：“我们意识到一个问题，该问题允许玩家的角色通过社交媒体上共享的恶意链接通过 Steam 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/amazon">Amazon</a>帐户链接成为目标。”</p><p>这些链接能够允许从另一个 Steam 帐户访问受害者的<em>Old School RuneScape</em>帐户，只要受害者在点击链接时登录了他们的<em>RuneScape</em>帐户。如果他们没有登录，系统会要求他们登录，并且不会弹出窗口来确保玩家不会将帐户交给未知的演员。</p><p>此外，有报道称这<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/2007scape/comments/15qp6w8/psa_there_seems_to_be_an_exploit_with_the_jagex/">也影响了 Jagex 帐户</a>，尽管开发者表示该漏洞与这些帐户无关。 </p><figure id="attachment_3473756" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3473756" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3473756" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Old-School-RuneScape-quest-Desert-Treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Old-School-RuneScape-quest-Desert-Treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Old-School-RuneScape-quest-Desert-Treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Old-School-RuneScape-quest-Desert-Treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Old-School-RuneScape-quest-Desert-Treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Old-School-RuneScape-quest-Desert-Treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Old-School-RuneScape-quest-Desert-Treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3473756" class="wp-caption-text"> “老派 RuneScape” 图片来源：Jagex</figcaption></figure><p> Jagex 继续说道：“虽然我们没有任何证据表明这对大量玩家产生了影响，但团队目前正在努力找出受此影响的任何帐户。”</p><p> “我们打算直接与个人联系，这意味着您不需要联系我们。我们还在探索可用的选项来退回因此而丢失的任何物品。”</p><p>开发人员决定关闭<em>Old School RuneScape</em>帐户与外部服务 Steam 和 Amazon 的链接功能，直到找到安全漏洞的解决方案。该团队总结道：“我们非常认真地对待这个问题，并希望尽快与您分享更多信息。”</p><p>在其他地方，玩家们也开始尝试<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/old-school-runescape-quest-desert-treasure-gets-a-sequel-after-18-years-3473743"><em>《沙漠宝藏 2 - 堕落帝国》</em></a> ，这是游戏中最受喜爱的任务线之一的续作。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/old-school-runescape-accounts-hijacked-to-transfer-them-to-hackers-3483282">“Old School RuneScape”帐户被劫持并转移给黑客的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
